flowchart TD
    User[User selects CCC import] --> Endpoint[POST /api/ccc/import-to-data-entry]
    Endpoint --> Access[Check user and company access]
    Access --> Resolve[Resolve selected projects]
    Resolve --> Client[CCC API client]
    Client --> PurchaseOrders[Fetch purchase orders]
    PurchaseOrders --> StatusFilter[Filter allowed purchase order statuses]
    StatusFilter --> Transform[Transform to Data Entry row shape]
    Transform --> Dedupe[Generate dedupe key]
    Dedupe --> Existing{Already imported}
    Existing -- Yes --> Skip[Skip row]
    Existing -- No --> Save[Write DataEntry cells]
    Save --> Notify[Create notification]
    Save --> Mapping{Auto mapping requested}
    Mapping -- Yes --> Job[Create mapping job]
    Mapping -- No --> Result[Return import counts]
    Job --> Result
    Skip --> Result
